annotationA: Ubiquinol-cytochrome-c reductase activity; metal ion binding; metalloendopeptidase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: proteolysis; protein processing; mitochondrial electron transport, ubiquinol to cytochrome c; cytoplasmic microtubule organization
annotationB: Cytochrome c oxidase subunit 3; Subunits I, II and III form the functional core of the enzyme complex
